---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative mt-20 pb-12 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[300px] bg-gradient-to-t from-purple-500/10 to-transparent blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/5 rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-16">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8">

                <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-[1000] italic uppercase tracking-tighter text-white">
                        TURBO<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-400 to-cyan-400">BLOCKS</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
                        Najwyższa jakość minigier w klimacie <span class="text-cyan-400">neon-futuristic</span>.
                        Stworzone z pasją przez Velocity Vale Studios dla najbardziej wymagających graczy.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl w-fit border border-white/5">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_10px_#22c55e]"></div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60">Server Status: Online</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-6">
                    <h4 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-pink-500">Navigation</h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li><a href="/regulamin" class="text-sm font-bold text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors">Regulamin</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/prywatnosc" class="text-sm font-bold text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors">Prywatność</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/pomoc" class="text-sm font-bold text-white/40 hover:text-white transition-colors">Centrum Pomocy</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
                    <h4 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-cyan-400">Legal</h4>
                    <p class="text-[10px] leading-relaxed text-white/20 uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter">
                        TurboBlocks is not an official Minecraft product. We are not approved by or associated with Mojang AB.
                        Wszelkie znaki towarowe należą do ich właścicieli.
                    </p>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            &copy; {currentYear} <span class="text-white">Velocity Vale Studios</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center px-8 gap-4">
            <div class="flex gap-6">
                <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-white/10 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Built with Astro & Qwik</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-[9px] font-bold text-white/10 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">
                Color Clash Season One // v2.0.0
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>